high_descs: Walk to the stove, turn right and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Wash the knife in the sink.
Turn all the way around to the right until you are at the small table in the corner.
Set the knife on the small table.
anns.task_desc: Wash the knife and put it away on the small table in the corner.

high_descs: Move forward then turn right walk towards the sink counter

Put the knife in the sink and rinse it
Pick up the knife then turn around to your left head towards the shelves to your left
Put the knife beside the salt shaker on top of the shelves
anns.task_desc: Put the clean knife on the shelves
